data.description: Beautiful townhome in the heart of Valencia! This Fairways Golf Course side Complex is in one of the most sought after neighborhoods in Valencia.  This home has 3 bedrooms 3 bathrooms with a finished attic that can be used as a bonus room or small bedroom!! You will find high vaulted ceilings that span around 20 ft in the living room and raised ceilings throughout. Amidst these plush greenbelts and golf course views there are 3 Pools, spas, 2 tennis courts, and a playground. Minutes from the 5 you are centrally located yet tucked away for privacy. This home is FHA approved and has an attached 2 car garage with direct access to the unit.   Newer HVAC installed in the last 4 years, well maintained.
